title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum on 1992-12-11

Cold Rain & Snow, Wang Dang Doodle, Althea, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Stagger Lee, Cassidy, Deal

Set 2

Iko Iko, Looks Like Rain, Eyes Of The World-> Corinna-> Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> Stella Blue-> Sugar Magnolia, E: U.S. Blues
